|FLAG|
  see $|$\|bit-flag\|$$ for explanaition on bit flags
  
  make number with single bit a set 
  1 << 0 0000
  1 << 1 0001
  1 << 2 0010
  1 << 3 0100
  1 << 4 1000
  aka. 1<<a == 2^a, 0, 2, 4, 8, ...
  
  \#define FLAG(a) (1 << (a)) 
