  see $|$\|bit-flag\|$$ for explanaition on bit flags
  
  check if flag a and b have a set bit in common
  a: 00010010
  b: 00000010
  &: 00000010 true bc. >1
  
  \#define HAS_FLAG(a, b)   ((a) & (b))
